Fallon-and-Travis-Kelce-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Jimmy-Fallon-and-Travis-Kelce-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Jimmy-Fallon-and-Travis-Kelce-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Jimmy-Fallon-and-Travis-Kelce-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/jimmy-fallon">Jimmy Fallon</a>和<a href="/artists/the-roots">Roots 乐队</a>的 Tariq “Black Thought” Trotter 将<a href="/artists/travis-kelce">Travis Kelce</a>的旧推文变成了音乐。</p><p>凯尔斯在 2008 年至 2018 年左右发布的旧推文最近在他与流行歌星<a href="/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift)</a>的高调恋情后疯传。作为<em>《今夜秀》</em>节目的一部分，法伦和 Black Thought 亲自将病毒式推文转化为音乐。</p><p>在题为“特拉维斯·凯尔斯之歌”的演讲中，Black Thought 总结了堪萨斯城酋长队近端锋的 X/Twitter 活动，而法伦则对推文进行了旁白。</p><p> <em>“有时他真的很深刻，他会激励整个世界/这个地球上最强大的武器是燃烧的人类灵魂/然后他会把它降低一个档次，把事情变得超级轻/去买一些塔可钟！！！看看今晚有什么流行音乐。“</em> </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="吉米和塔里克·特罗特表演“特拉维斯·凯尔斯之歌”|今夜秀" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Mb1aU07Eobw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>谈到凯尔斯和斯威夫特的关系，公众认知和公关专家贝丝·布克（Beth Booker）说：“我们正在实时看到这段浪漫的故事，我认为这就是为什么每个人都如此支持它。自从第一个关于他们的小面包屑以来，我们就一直在一起。” （ <a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/jimmy-fallon-black-thought-travis-kelce-tweets-song-1234886479/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>滚石杂志</em></a>）</p><p>在其他消息中，费城的一家广播电台暂时禁止斯威夫特的音乐<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swifts-music-temporarily-banned-in-philadelphia-ahead-of-travis-kelce-game-3543382">，直到特拉维斯·凯尔斯的堪萨斯城酋长队来访之后</a>。</p><p>酋长队定于周一（11 月 20 日）在 NFL 比赛中对阵费城老鹰队，当地 Q102 电台表示，至少在周二之前不会播放与凯尔斯有恋情的斯威夫特的歌曲。</p><p> “Q102 整个周末都在广播电台中支持泰勒·斯威夫特，因为虽然 Q102 很喜欢泰勒·斯威夫特，但我们对她的喜爱程度不够，这个周末我们对小鸟队表示支持非常重要，”其中一名成员 Nugget 说道。电台主持人， <a href="https://www.cbsnews.com/philadelphia/news/taylor-swift-chiefs-eagles-philadelphia-radio-station-q012/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>哥伦比亚广播公司新闻费城</i></a>。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CyL5v84rvtJ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.